Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:08.98,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,So that's where... you were... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:12.45,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You... were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:16.21,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,In that{Obviously we want to avoid using gendered pronouns here because if we say "his" body then that's already giving away too much. -Starfish} body...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:21.14,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The moment I started feeling tired \N and my soul began leaving my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:26.92,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...you said you had to go \Nsince things weren't going well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:28.80,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You were right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.97,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,If you're there, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.57,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...I know for sure that we'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.39,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.29,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...I feel so alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:46.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Will you... call me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.86,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...like you always have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:52.48,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Boss...
